object.customQuery:
select

a."Policy Key" as Policy_Key
,"Policy Key Code"  as Policy_Key_Code
,"Policy Coverage Code"  as Policy_Coverage_Code
,AnnualStatementLineCd as Annual_Statement_Line
,StatLineCd  as Stat_Line_Cd
,"Risk State ID" as Risk_State_ID
,"Agency ID"  as Agency_ID
,"Major Peril ID" as Major_Peril_ID
,cast(TO_TIMESTAMP("Time",'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')as timestamp) as Dim_Time
,NULL as "Inforce Premium"
,coalesce("SAR Premium", 0) as "SAR Premium"
,coalesce("Commission Amount", 0) as "Commission Amount"
,coalesce("Taxes Service Charges", 0) as "Taxes Service Charges"
,NULL as "Earned Premium"
,NULL as "Unearned Premium"
,NULL as "Written Commission Fee Amt"
,NULL as "Written Premium Fee Amt"
,NULL as "Inforce Policy Key"
,CoverageCd
,"Quoted Premium"
,RateAreaName
 FROM

 (SELECT "Policy Key"
,"Policy Key Code"
,"Policy Coverage Code"
,"Risk State ID"
,"Agency ID"
,"Major Peril ID"
,"Time"
,AnnualStatementLineCd
,StatLineCd
,CoverageCd
,SUM("SAR Premium") "SAR Premium"
,SUM("Commission Amount") "Commission Amount"
,SUM("Taxes Service Charges") "Taxes Service Charges"
,SUM(QuotedPremium) "Quoted Premium"
,RateAreaNAme
FROM
(SELECT
B.CarrierCd+B.PolicyKey as "Policy Key"
,B.CarrierCd+B.PolicyKey+A.RiskId as "Policy Key Code"
,CAST(a.PolicyKey+coalesce(a.RiskId,'')+a.CoverageId AS varchar(100)) as "Policy Coverage Code"
,A.PolicyKey+A.RiskId AS "Risk State ID"
,coalesce(dd.AgencyCd,D.AgencyCd) AS "Agency ID"
,A.MajorperilCd AS "Major Peril ID"
,DATE_TRUNC('month', A.TransactionAccountingDt) AS "Time"

,A.WrittenCommissionAmt as "Commission Amount"
,A.Taxesandservicecharges AS "Taxes Service Charges"
,A.WrittenPremiumAmt AS "SAR Premium"
,'Guidewire' AS "Data Source"
,A.AnnualStatementLineCd
,A.StatLineCd
,A.CoverageCd
,A.QuotedPremium
,a.rateareaname
FROM dbo.PolicyTransaction A
LEFT JOIN dbo.PolicyDetail B   on A.PolicyKey = B.PolicyKey
left join (select distinct AgentCd,AgencyCd from dbo.Agents   where RowEffEndDt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000') d
on d.AgentCd = B.ProviderNumber
left join (select distinct AgentCd,AgencyCd from dbo.Agents   where RowEffEndDt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000') dd
on dd.AgentCd = a.AgentId
where A.RowEffEndDt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
and A.BookDt < cast(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP as date)
) A
GROUP BY "Policy Key"
,"Policy Key Code"
,"Policy Coverage Code"
,"Risk State ID"
,"Agency ID"
,"Major Peril ID"
,"Time"
,AnnualStatementLineCd
,StatLineCd
,CoverageCd
,rateareaname
)a

UNION ALL

select

COALESCE( d."Policy Key",b."Policy Key") as Policy_Key
,COALESCE(d."Policy Key Code",b."Policy Key Code" ) as Policy_Key_Code
,COALESCE(d."Policy Coverage Code",b."Policy Coverage Code") as Policy_Coverage_Code
,COALESCE(d.AnnualStatementLineCd,b.AnnualStatementLineCd) as Annual_Statement_Line
,COALESCE(d.StatLineCd,b.StatLineCd) as Stat_Line_Cd
,COALESCE(d."Risk State ID",b."Risk State ID") as Risk_State_ID
,COALESCE(d."Agency ID",b."Agency ID") as Agency_ID
,COALESCE(d."Major Peril ID",b."Major Peril ID") as Major_Peril_ID
,COALESCE(d."Time",b."Time") as Dim_Time
,coalesce("Inforce Premium", 0) as "Inforce Premium"
,null as "SAR Premium"
,NULL as "Commission Amount"
,NULL as "Taxes Service Charges"
,coalesce("Earned Premium", 0) as "Earned Premium"
,coalesce("Unearned Premium", 0) as "Unearned Premium"
,coalesce("Written Commission Fee Amt", 0) as "Written Commission Fee Amt"
,coalesce("Written Premium Fee Amt", 0) as "Written Premium Fee Amt"
,"Inforce Policy Key"
,coalesce(d.CoverageCd,b.coverageCd) as CoverageCd
,NULL as "Quoted Premium"
,coalesce(d. rateareaname,b.rateAReaName) as RateAreaName
from
(
SELECT "Policy Key"
,"Policy Key Code"
,"Policy Coverage Code"
,"Risk State ID"
,"Agency ID"
,"Major Peril ID"
,cast(TO_TIMESTAMP("Time",'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')as timestamp) as "Time"
,AnnualStatementLineCd
,StatLineCd
,CoverageCd
,RateAreaName
,SUM("Earned Premium") AS "Earned Premium"
,SUM("Unearned Premium") AS "Unearned Premium"
,SUM("Written Premium Fee Amt") AS "Written Premium Fee Amt"
,SUM("Written Commission Fee Amt") AS "Written Commission Fee Amt"
FROM
(
    SELECT
CAST(B.CarrierCd+B.PolicyKey AS varchar(100)) AS "Policy Key"
,CAST(B.CarrierCd+B.PolicyKey+A.RiskId AS varchar(100)) AS "Policy Key Code"
,CAST(A.PolicyKey+coalesce(A.RiskId,'')+A.CoverageId AS varchar(100)) as "Policy Coverage Code"
,CAST(A.PolicyKey+A.RiskId AS varchar(100)) AS "Risk State ID"
,coalesce(dd.Agencycd,D.AgencyCd) AS "Agency ID"
,A.MajorperilCd AS "Major Peril ID"
,TO_TIMESTAMP(SUBSTRING(ReportPeriod, 1, 4) || '-' || SUBSTRING(ReportPeriod, 5, 2) || '-01', 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS "Time"
,A.MTDEarnedPremiumAmount AS "Earned Premium"
,A.UNearnedPremiumAmount AS "Unearned Premium"
, A.MTDWrittenCommissionFeeAmt AS "Written Commission Fee Amt"
, A. MTDWrittenPremiumFeeAmt AS "Written Premium Fee Amt"
,'Guidewire' AS "Data Source"
,A.AnnualStatementLineCd
,A.StatLineCd
,A.CoverageCd
,A.RateAreaName
FROM dbo.EarnedPremiumFact A
LEFT JOIN dbo.PolicyDetail B    ON A.PolicyKey = B.PolicyKey
LEFT JOIN (select distinct agentcd,agencycd from dbo.agents  where RowEffEndDt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000') D
ON D.AgentCd = B.ProviderNumber
LEFT JOIN (select distinct agentcd,agencycd from dbo.agents  where RowEffEndDt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000') DD
ON Dd.AgentCd = a.AgentId

) B
GROUP BY "Policy Key"
,"Policy Key Code"
,"Policy Coverage Code"
,"Risk State ID"
,"Agency ID"
,"Major Peril ID"
,"Time"
,AnnualStatementLineCd
,StatLineCd
,CoverageCd
,RateAreaName
) b

full outer join

(SELECT
          c.CarrierCd+A.policykey AS "Policy Key"
,c.CarrierCd+A.policykey AS "Inforce Policy Key"
         ,c.CarrierCd+A.policykey+A.RiskId AS "Policy Key Code"
        ,CAST(a.PolicyKey+coalesce(a.RiskId,'')+a.CoverageId AS varchar(100)) as "Policy Coverage Code"
        ,a.majorperilcd AS "Major Peril ID"
         ,a.PolicyKey+a.RiskId AS "Risk State ID"
        ,coalesce(gg.agencycd, g.AgencyCd) AS "Agency ID"
         ,d.dimid AS "Inforce TimeID"
        ,d.calendar_dt AS "Accident Time"
        ,cast(TO_TIMESTAMP(d.calendar_dt,'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')as timestamp)  AS "Time"
        ,SUM(a.InforcedAmount) AS "Inforce Premium"
        ,'Guidewire' AS "Data Source"
        ,A.AnnualStatementLineCd
        ,a.StatLineCd
        ,CoverageCd
        ,RateAreaName
FROM dbo.earnedpremiumfact a
inner join
(select CarrierCd,PolicyKey,ProviderNumber,CONCAT(SUBSTRING(TO_CHAR(PolicyEffectiveDt, 'YYYYMMDD'), 1, 6), '01') as PolicyStartDt,
                                            case when PolicyCancelDt is null then CONCAT(SUBSTRING(TO_CHAR(PolicyExpirationDt, 'YYYYMMDD'), 1, 6), '01')

else CONCAT(SUBSTRING(TO_CHAR(PolicyCancelDt, 'YYYYMMDD'), 1, 6), '01')
  end as PolicyEndDt, policysystemid from dbo.policydetail
                                      ) c
on  a.policykey = c.policykey
left join (select distinct agentcd,agencycd from dbo.Agents where RowEffEndDt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000') g
on c.ProviderNumber = g.AgentCd
left join  (select dimid,calendar_dt,concat(left(period,4),right(period,2)) as reportperiod from dbo.view_dim_time) d
on  d.reportperiod = a.reportperiod
left join (select distinct agentcd,agencycd from dbo.Agents where RowEffEndDt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000') gg
on gg.AgentCd =a.AgentId
where  TO_CHAR(d.calendar_dt, 'YYYYMMDD') < c.PolicyEndDt

GROUP BY c.CarrierCd,A.policykey,A.RiskId,a.CoverageId,A.AnnualStatementLineCd,coalesce(gg.agencycd, g.AgencyCd),a.majorperilcd, d.dimid, d.calendar_dt
,a.AnnualStatementLineCd,a.StatLineCd,CoverageCd,RateAreaName
) d
on B."Policy Key"=d."Policy Key"
and b."Policy Key Code" =d."Policy Key Code"
and b."Policy Coverage Code"=d."Policy Coverage Code"
and b.AnnualStatementLineCd=d.AnnualStatementLineCd
and b.StatLineCd=d.StatLineCd
and b.CoverageCd=d.CoverageCd
and b."Risk State ID"=d."Risk State ID"
and b."Agency ID"=d."Agency ID"
and b."Major Peril ID"=d."Major Peril ID"
and b.RateAreaName=d.RateAreaName
and b."Time"=d."Time"
